lyrics:
[Verse]
Sitting in his office, papers all around
Brandon's working hard, tax season's in town
Numbers and forms, they're driving him insane
But he won't give up, he'll conquer this campaign

[Chorus]
Oh, Brandon, take a break and let go
Dance around the office, let your worries flow
Oh, Brandon, just take a breath and breathe
Let the rhythm guide you, let your soul believe
